# VE475 Homework5 ex4

## RSA encryption and decryption

All the codes are in the file ```ex4.cpp```, which contains three functions ```generate```, ```encrypt``` and ```decrypt```. It also contains a ```main()``` function to perform RSA encryption and decryption in all kinds of securities.

* For execution of the file, you can just run ```./ex4``` in the terminal, and it will ask you to input a plaintext, feel free to type in any plaintext you like.
* If there is something wrong with the execution file ```ex4```, there is also a ```Makefile``` attached, you can run ```make``` to generate another execution file.
* If ```Makefile``` goes wrong, there is a ```CMakeList```, please run ```cmake ./``` in the folder ```ex4``` to generate another ```Makefile```, and do the above procedures.
